data.title: 40 Days and 40 Nights on the Camino de Santiago with Jamie, The Long Distance Coach
data.meta_description: Listen to 40 Days and 40 Nights on the Camino de Santiago with Jamie, The Long Distance Coach on Spotify. A personal journal of struggles, miracles and overcoming adversity. The podcast follows my journey through life and my experience of walking the EPIC 500-mile St James' Way and the shorter English Way of the Camino de Santiago.
